quran[8{c,v,t}:
10,54,"agar har uss shakhs ke paas jis ne zulm kya hai, Roye zameen ki doulat bhi ho to uss azaab se bachney ke liye woh usay Fidya mein dainay par amaada ho jaye ga jab yeh log is azaab ko dekh len ge to dil hi dil mein puchta-ayn ge magar un ke darmain poooray insaaf se faisla kya jaye ga koi zulm un par nah ho ga"
10,55,suno! asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai Allah ka hai sun rakho! Allah ka wada schcha hai magar aksar ensaan jantay nahi hain
10,56,wohi zindagi bkhshta hai aur wohi mout deta hai aur isi ki taraf tum sab ko palatna hai
10,57,logo! tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se nasiyaat aa gayi hai yeh woh cheez hai jo dilon ke amraaz ki Shifa hai aur jo usay qubool kar len un ke liye rahnumai aur rehmat hai
10,58,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho ke “ih Allah ka fazl aur is ki meharbani hai ke yeh cheez is ne bhaije, is par to logon ko khusi mnanai chahiye, yeh unn sab cheezon se behtar hai jinhein log samaitt rahay hain """
10,59,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho “تم logon ne kabhi yeh bhi socha hai ke jo rizaq Allah ne tumahray liye utaara tha is mein se tum ne khud hi kisi ko haraam aur kisi ko halaltehra liya !"" inn se pucho, Allah ne tum ko is ki ijazat di thi? ya tum Allah par aftara kar rahay ho ?"
10,60,jo log Allah par yeh jhoota aftara bandhte hain un ka kya gumaan hai ke qayamat ke roz un se kya maamla ho ga? Allah to logon par meharbani ki nazar rakhta hai magar aksar ensaan aisay hain jo shukar nahi karte
10,61,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum jis haal mein bhi hotay ho aur quran mein se jo kuch bhi sanatay ho, aur logo, tum bhi jo kuch karte ho uss sab ke douran mein hum tum ko dekhte rehtay hain koi zarra barabar cheez aasman aur zameen mein aisi nahi hai, nah choti nah barri, jo tairay rab ki nazar se posheeda ho aur aik saaf daftar mein darj nah ho"
